query:
update car set
                    chassis = $2,
                    make = $3,
                    model = $4,
                    registration = $5,
                    plate = $6,
                    year = $7,
                    engine_displacement_litres = $8,
                    mileage_km = $9,
                    unladen_weight = $10,
                    laden_weight = $11,
                    seats = $12
                where id = $1
